01:28.002 --> 01:29.468
[ sniffles ]

01:44.617 --> 01:46.283
I hope
you got good sleep.

01:46.285 --> 01:48.118
We're gonna need
all of that charm of yours

01:48.120 --> 01:49.519
For the day
we've got planned.

01:49.521 --> 01:51.621
Well, seems to have worked
on everybody so far, hasn't it?

01:51.623 --> 01:54.590
Well...
<i> Almost</i> everybody.

01:54.592 --> 01:56.224
[ both chuckle ]

01:56.226 --> 01:59.794
