25:56.896 --> 25:58.695
That whole juliette episode
this morning

25:58.697 --> 25:59.996
Was a nonissue.

25:59.998 --> 26:01.964
Well, I guess I ought to
give him a hug, too.

26:01.966 --> 26:03.065
[ laughs ]

26:03.067 --> 26:05.634
Actually, I was thinking
of something else.

26:05.636 --> 26:07.068
What's that?

26:07.070 --> 26:08.202
The c.E.O. Job.

26:08.204 --> 26:10.037
I thought we already
talked about that.

26:10.039 --> 26:11.004
