26:11.006 --> 26:12.772
But now I'm asking you
to reconsider.

26:14.342 --> 26:15.808
[ rapid knocks on door ]

26:16.844 --> 26:18.009
Have you seen the news?

26:18.011 --> 26:19.176
Yeah, I just --

26:19.178 --> 26:20.877
