[ chuckles ] no.

27:12.950 --> 27:15.116
Hey, and I got to thank maddie.
Girl, you unlocked it.

27:15.118 --> 27:16.584
[ laughs ]

27:16.586 --> 27:18.085
Can we go home now?

27:19.555 --> 27:22.088
In all the years
I've had this bar,

27:22.090 --> 27:24.290
Beverly's night
was always my best.

27:24.292 --> 27:25.858
Is that right?

27:25.860 --> 27:27.693
She was
a born performer.

27:27.695 --> 27:29.761
She was that.
Yeah.

27:29.763 --> 27:31.896
It's just too bad
this is natchez

27:31.898 --> 27:33.898
And not nashville.

27:33.900 --> 27:36.200
Woman: Your mother
used to come into my salon,

27:36.202 --> 27:39.369
Sit in my chair, and brag on you
till the moment she left.

27:39.371 --> 27:40.870
About what?

27:40.872 --> 27:43.305
Well, how you were out on tour
with luke wheeler

27:43.307 --> 27:45.573
Or opening
for rascal flatts.

27:45.575 --> 27:47.408
And then
there was a clip of you

27:47.410 --> 27:50.244
With some fella named gunnar
on the internet?

27:50.246 --> 27:52.746
She must have played it for me
a dozen times.

27:52.748 --> 27:53.947
Really?

27:53.949 --> 27:56.883
You know, no one
was supposed to sing tonight,

27:56.885 --> 27:59.785
But that was when
nobody knew<i> you</i> were coming.

27:59.787 --> 28:01.419
Would you consider
singing something?

28:01.421 --> 28:03.921
Uh, do you think
that would be appropriate?

28:03.923 --> 28:07.591
Dear, I think
it would be perfect.

28:07.593 --> 28:08.825
Told you
this would be fun.

28:08.827 --> 28:10.927
Yeah, hanging out with
a bunch of stuffy, old people

28:10.929 --> 28:12.094
Instead of my girlfriend.

28:12.096 --> 28:13.228
Time of my life.

28:13.230 --> 28:14.495
You know what?

28:14.497 --> 28:17.698
Why don't you try
and enjoy yourself a little bit?

28:21.903 --> 28:23.535
I'll enjoy<i> this.</i>

28:24.771 --> 28:26.771
Luke: Hey, y'all.
Hey.

28:26.773 --> 28:28.439
You certainly went
all-out.

28:28.441 --> 28:29.773
Well,
I got a lot to celebrate.

28:29.775 --> 28:32.008
Uh, listen.

28:32.010 --> 28:34.010
I know you were interested
in the c.E.O. Position.

28:34.012 --> 28:37.579
I also know I haven't
always trusted you, jeff.

28:39.316 --> 28:42.516
But today, you more than proved
your commitment to me.

28:43.919 --> 28:44.918
Welcome aboard.

28:44.920 --> 28:45.785
[ laughs ]

28:45.787 --> 28:47.086
Thank you.

28:47.088 --> 28:48.320
I won't let you down.
No, I know.

28:48.322 --> 28:49.587
Have fun tonight.

28:49.589 --> 28:50.754
Tomorrow, we start talking
about the future.

28:50.756 --> 28:51.788
All right.
All right.

28:51.790 --> 28:53.523
