28:53.525 --> 28:55.258
You did it!

28:55.260 --> 28:56.359
[ both laugh ]

28:56.361 --> 28:58.094
I'm so proud of you.
Thank you.

28:58.096 --> 28:59.161
Better call the movers.

28:59.163 --> 29:01.295
Already did.

29:03.465 --> 29:05.531
[ scoffs ]

29:05.533 --> 29:06.999
You all right?

29:07.001 --> 29:08.500
[ scoffs ]

29:10.003 --> 29:13.537
Did you<i> not</i> see those girls
push that gay guy up front,

29:13.539 --> 29:15.605
