a little dramatic.

29:31.118 --> 29:32.784
No, I'm not.

29:34.387 --> 29:36.586
My dream is dead.

29:39.223 --> 29:40.622
What do you want me to say,
will?

29:40.624 --> 29:42.957
Don't say anything.

29:44.393 --> 29:46.559
