with you.

30:00.337 --> 30:01.602
We're done.

30:11.680 --> 30:13.246
[ indistinct conversations ]

30:13.248 --> 30:15.314
Good evening,
ladies and gentlemen.

30:15.316 --> 30:17.416
And for those of you that
I haven't gotten to meet yet,

30:17.418 --> 30:18.850
I'm scarlett.

30:18.852 --> 30:20.017
I'm beverly's daughter.

30:20.019 --> 30:21.885
[ cheers and applause ]

