33:21.562 --> 33:23.228
Okay, well,
what you did today

33:23.230 --> 33:25.964
Was your interpretation
of his song.

33:25.966 --> 33:27.832
It was from<i> you.</i>
It was from your heart.

33:27.834 --> 33:29.733
What you did last night
was something else.

33:29.735 --> 33:33.069
It was...Not reflective of you
or who you want to be.

33:33.071 --> 33:34.436
Whatever you say, mom.

33:37.307 --> 33:38.806
Hey, one more thing.
Hmm?

33:40.543 --> 33:42.776
Daphne's been having
a tough time.

33:44.513 --> 33:46.513
I think she really wanted
to sing with you today.

33:46.515 --> 33:48.414
How was I supposed to know that
she was gonna change her mind?

33:48.416 --> 33:51.016
You weren't. You weren't.
I'm just...

33:51.018 --> 33:53.485
I just want you to be aware
so that you can try

33:53.487 --> 33:55.753
To be more considerate
of her feelings -- that's all.

33:55.755 --> 33:57.554
Why should I care
what<i> you</i> want

33:57.556 --> 33:59.922
When you do not care
what<i> I</i> want?

34:02.927 --> 34:06.028
¶ every little thing you do
is a small reminder ¶

34:06.030 --> 34:08.263
You know,
all these years,

34:08.265 --> 34:10.865
I thought mama resented me
for my career.

34:10.867 --> 34:12.833
¶ is you
upon the mountain peak ¶

34:12.835 --> 34:14.801
'cause I had something
she wanted so bad and never got.

34:18.206 --> 34:19.905
Turns out
she was proud of me.

34:19.907 --> 34:21.239
¶ looking out
over all of shenandoah ¶

34:21.241 --> 34:23.941
She still is, too,
sweetheart.

34:23.943 --> 34:27.044
I know she was smiling down
from above tonight.

34:27.046 --> 34:29.613
¶ the rocks below... ¶

34:29.615 --> 34:32.449
I'm gonna do that tour
with gunnar.

34:32.451 --> 34:34.083
It's what she would have
wanted for me.

34:34.085 --> 34:36.718
So I'm gonna do it
for her.

34:36.720 --> 34:38.720
Well, good.

34:38.722 --> 34:41.455
I'm glad
you made me stay.

34:43.025 --> 34:44.424
Me too.

34:44.426 --> 34:47.593
Now I know how much
she meant to that place...

34:49.563 --> 34:51.696
