sorry!

35:01.539 --> 35:03.605
Hey! There you are.
Haven't seen you.

35:03.607 --> 35:05.773
Yeah, I've just been around,
having fun, like you said.

35:05.775 --> 35:06.907
You all right?

35:06.909 --> 35:08.575
Yeah, I'm just tired.
I'm gonna go to bed.

35:08.577 --> 35:10.343
Okay.

35:11.646 --> 35:12.911
Amazing night.

35:12.913 --> 35:15.413
Quite possibly
the best ever.

35:15.415 --> 35:17.181
What do you say
we go celebrate alone?

35:18.417 --> 35:21.317
Uh, I should probably stay here
for a little bit longer.

35:21.319 --> 35:23.552
You go.
I'll be down soon.

35:23.554 --> 35:25.420
Okay.
Take your time.

35:25.422 --> 35:28.122
If I'm asleep when you get in,
just wake me.

35:28.124 --> 35:29.523
[ both chuckle ]

35:38.000 --> 35:40.166
[ breathing shakily ]

35:43.737 --> 35:45.403
[ crying ]

36:00.185 --> 36:02.151
[ crying continues ]

36:07.524 --> 36:10.224
[ cellphone clatters ]

36:12.194 --> 36:14.060
[ cellphone chimes ]

37:01.141 --> 37:02.974
[ cellphone rings ]

37:02.976 --> 37:03.975
Hey.

37:03.977 --> 37:05.843
Hey, hold on a sec.

37:05.845 --> 37:07.678
I'm not catching you
too late, am I?

37:07.680 --> 37:09.312
Never too late
if you need to talk.

37:09.314 --> 37:10.680
You all right?

37:10.682 --> 37:12.181
Actually, yeah.

37:12.183 --> 37:14.850
I'm -- I'm pretty good.

37:14.852 --> 37:16.484
So what's up?

37:16.486 --> 37:18.853
Well, I've been thinking
about that bar of yours.

37:18.855 --> 37:21.155
I know you've been having
some trouble keeping her going.

37:21.157 --> 37:22.256
You're right about that.

37:22.258 --> 37:23.857
Well,
I think I might have

37:23.859 --> 37:26.325
