a little bit, and I, uh...

37:28.195 --> 37:29.594
...I want to buy in.

37:29.596 --> 37:31.429
You serious?

37:31.431 --> 37:33.898
[ chuckling ]
I am, yeah.

37:33.900 --> 37:36.066
I was wondering if I could make
one request, though.

37:36.068 --> 37:37.033
What's that?

37:37.035 --> 37:38.601
That we rename the place.

37:38.603 --> 37:41.704
How do you feel about...

37:41.706 --> 37:43.439
"the beverly"?

37:45.176 --> 37:46.575
Luke: All right,
thanks for coming, y'all.

37:46.577 --> 37:48.443
