take a minute.

38:01.555 --> 38:03.588
All right.
Suit yourself, c.E.O.

38:14.733 --> 38:16.532
[ lock beeps, disengages ]

38:18.602 --> 38:22.603
Well, I guess
everything worked out perfectly.

38:22.605 --> 38:24.271
You really not
gonna invite me in?

38:24.273 --> 38:26.039
I told you --

38:26.041 --> 38:28.708
There are lines I don't cross
when it comes to clients.

38:28.710 --> 38:29.675
Fair enough.

38:31.045 --> 38:32.210
You're fired.

38:32.212 --> 38:33.578
[ laughing ] really?

38:33.580 --> 38:34.912
After everything
I've done for you?

38:34.914 --> 38:36.213
Oh,
it's just for tonight.

38:36.215 --> 38:39.149
I plan on hiring you back
first thing in the morning.

38:44.990 --> 38:46.856
[ cellphone buzzing ]

38:51.929 --> 38:53.962
[ buzzing continues ]

38:55.966 --> 38:56.965
Hello?

38:56.967 --> 38:58.900
Hey, it's me.

38:58.902 --> 39:00.234
Maddie?

39:00.236 --> 39:01.735
Yeah.
I took daphne's phone.

39:01.737 --> 39:03.069
Hey.

39:03.071 --> 39:04.770
Nice to hear from you.

39:04.772 --> 39:07.239
Are you okay?
You sound weird.

39:07.241 --> 39:09.774
Um...

39:09.776 --> 39:11.876
Yeah -- you mind
if I actually call you back?

39:12.778 --> 39:13.943
Sure.

39:13.945 --> 39:14.677
Okay.

39:18.648 --> 39:19.980
Ugh.

39:29.758 --> 39:31.591
[ horns honking ]

39:40.101 --> 39:42.668
Avery:
<i> I can't have her grow up</i>

39:42.670 --> 39:44.970
<i> Thinking that she can depend</i>
<i> on her mother</i>

39:44.972 --> 39:46.972
<i> When we both know</i>
<i> that she can't.</i>

39:46.974 --> 39:51.609
Juliette: [ crying ]
<i> I lost everything</i>
<i> that meant anything to me.</i>

39:51.611 --> 39:54.311
<i> I'm just stuck</i>
<i> being stupid, screwed-up me!</i>

39:54.313 --> 39:56.613
Jeff:<i> ...A one-time bang</i>
<i> in a broom closet, sweetheart.</i>

39:56.615 --> 39:58.848
Juliette: [ distorted ]
<i> you don't need to remind me</i>
<i> of the mistakes I've made.</i>

39:58.850 --> 40:00.783
